=head1 DESCRIPTION

Provides information for updating the user on the progress of
fulfilling an intent.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Active => Bool

Determines whether fulfillment updates are sent to the user. When this
field is true, updates are sent.

If the C<active> field is set to true, the C<startResponse>,
C<updateResponse>, and C<timeoutInSeconds> fields are required.


=head2 StartResponse => L<Paws::LexModelsV2::FulfillmentStartResponseSpecification>

Provides configuration information for the message sent to users when
the fulfillment Lambda functions starts running.


=head2 TimeoutInSeconds => Int

The length of time that the fulfillment Lambda function should run
before it times out.


=head2 UpdateResponse => L<Paws::LexModelsV2::FulfillmentUpdateResponseSpecification>

Provides configuration information for messages sent periodically to
